109
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:09,680
- All right, let's drink.
- What?

110
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:12,470
I'm all yours today.

111
00:11:15,090 --> 00:11:17,490
You don't have work today anyway, right?

112
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:21,880
<i>[Nekoyanagi - Closed]</i>

113
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:24,890
<i>A divorce?</i>

114
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:27,890
But we have to talk about it, though.

115
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,710
You're right.

116
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,860
It's going to be hard.

117
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:43,130
I'll accept whatever choice Hiroki makes.

118
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:49,760
So, you haven't changed your mind, right?

119
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,230
Yeah.

120
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,820
But...

121
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:59,490
No matter what, you mustn't let go of Shiori-chan.

122
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:06,090
Miwa-san, you already went through so much to protect Shiori-chan.

123
