If I were in your shoes,

124
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:21,580
I probably would have done the same thing.

125
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,590
What?

126
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:27,900
I know it's something that should never be done,

127
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:31,970
