128
00:12:33,410 --> 00:12:36,580
I understand why you want to protect her.

129
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,820
Back then,

130
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:47,190
Shiori was the most precious to me.

131
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:52,790
But right now, it's not just her.

132
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:57,250
By that, you mean Hiroki-san, too?

133
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:05,620
Even so, you still mustn't leave Shiori-chan.

134
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:10,890
I mean, you can't bring yourself to leave her, can you?

135
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:18,600
From now on,

136
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:23,620
I have to think about what I can do for Shiori.

137
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,150
Of course.

138
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:33,220
Shall we have some sweet snacks?

139
00:13:33,830 --> 00:13:35,820
Makoto.

140
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,680
Yes?

141
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:40,410
I have a favor to ask of you.

142
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:42,420
What is it?

143
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:49,370
That's...

144
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:54,220
I can't keep this letter,

145
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:56,890
