146
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:06,090
I certainly have accepted Fuyutsuki-kun's feelings.

147
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:32,770
<i>- Is this okay?
- I think you should cut it down further.</i>

148
00:14:36,330 --> 00:14:38,110
<i>You did your best.</i>

149
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:41,020
<i>Aw, don't cry...</i>

150
